给你：

/* 移动小部件按钮 */
@media（最大宽度：768像素）{
  #Avada FAQ_Widget。阿瓦达Faqs_Button {
    底部：5 REM;
  }

  #Avada FAQ_Widget。Avada常见问题欢迎弹窗 {
    底部：9rem ！重要;
  }
}

/* move up widget button on mobile */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  #Avada-FAQ_Widget .Avada-Faqs_Button {
    bottom: 5rem;
  }

  #Avada-FAQ_Widget .Avada-FaqsWelcomePopup {
    bottom: 9rem !important;
  }
}

Ah you can try to follow these steps: Go to Chatbox > Advanced settings > Add the css code below to display only with the store language you want

.Avada-Faqs_Button {
display: none;
}

html[lang="de"] .Avada-Faqs_Button {
display: block !important;
}

if you want to display on the language you want other than Dutch, then duplicate this code and replace it with the language they want

html[lang="Language symbols"] .Avada-Faqs_Button {
display: block !important;
}
